Sharing: please note that you can only share your data openly on OSF if you are sure that it is fully anonymous, if data is pseudonymous, i.e. if there is still a (small) possibility that the participants could be reidentified by you or by others, please use RDR and apply access restrictions so interested researchers will have to submit a request to access the files upon signing a Data Transfer Agreement. You can use the integration dashboard to upload your OSF data to RDR see https://www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/rdr/integration-dashboard
